"### The Red Bird of the South (Summer)\n"
"\n"
"The 7 Moon Stations of the \"South\" or \"Red Bird\".\n"
"\n"
"|<notr>#</notr>|Chinese Character|Meaning|Key Star|Japanese Name|\n"
"|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|-----------------|-------|--------|-------------|\n"
"|<notr>22</notr>|![](mn22.png)|Well|<notr>&mu; Gem</notr>|"
